onBindOnNewForm

protected void onBindOnNewForm(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                               java.lang.Object cmd)
                        throws java.lang.Exception
This method will do the following, make the command to be in a consistent state. If from Review Report page? 1.- If this is a new data collection: 1.1. Create Expedited Report, associate it with Reporting period. 1.2. Initialize the Treatment information 1.3. Initialize the reporter. 2. Add/Remove adverse events. 3. Find the mandatory sections. 4. Pre-initialize the mandatory section fields. If from Manage reports page? 1. Find the mandatory sections 2. Refresh/Initialize the Not applicable and mandatory fields.
